title: Introducing the RCT by Nick Garcia
description:
A talented skateboarder and photographer, Nick Garcia combined his two passions on his new signature colorway of the etnies RCT. Nick's RCT takes inspiration and elements from his Canon AE-1 35mm camera on the heels of the shoes showing the focus and aperture markings, and on the footbeds highlighting a filmstrip and his photography. Even the etnies RAP bar on the side of the shoe is modeled after the leather wrapped body of his camera.
The Nick Garcia RCT (black/white) is available now on etnies.com and at finer skate shops globally.
See more of Nick's photography and the etnies RCT at http://etni.es/nick-garcia-rct
